    # m "Hey! What're you looking at?"
    m "嗨，你在看什麼？"

# game/day2.rpy:1128
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_62b80cba:

    # p "Your eyes only."
    p "你的眼睛。"

# game/day2.rpy:1130
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_9a1dd800:

    # p "So... Excited about the career day tomorrow?"
    p "所以……對明天的事業日有什麼想法？"

# game/day2.rpy:1132
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_a79d31cd:

    # m "I just hope it's going to be helpful for my future!"
    m "希望它會對我的未來有所幫助！"

# game/day2.rpy:1133
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_43955282:

    # p "I see. By the way, what do you plan to do?"
    p "知道了。順便說一下，你打算做什麼？"

# game/day2.rpy:1135
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_112b667a:

    # m "Huh?"
    m "嗯？"

# game/day2.rpy:1136
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_9621b446:

    # p "I mean, what are your plans for the future?"
    p "我的意思是，你對自己的未來有什麼計劃？"

# game/day2.rpy:1138
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_c2c6e530:

    # m "Hm... I can foresee myself getting a bachelor degree."
    m "啊……我想先讀大學本科。"

# game/day2.rpy:1139
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_446ab7c7:

    # p "C'mon, you know what I mean... What about after you graduate?"
    p "拜托，你知道我是什麼意思……畢業后呢？"

# game/day2.rpy:1141
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_635335a4:

    # m "I'm going to land one of the most prestigious entry-level jobs."
    m "我要找到500強公司的實習工作。"

# game/day2.rpy:1143
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_be344ca7:

    # p "What kind of a job is that?"
    p "什麼樣的工作？"

# game/day2.rpy:1145
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_90662a65:

    # m "Either investment banking or consulting."
    m "投資金融或者咨詢。"

# game/day2.rpy:1146
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_e15bcf71:

    # p "Right, I've heard it's very exciting to work there."
    p "不錯。我聽說那邊的工作很有趣。"

# game/day2.rpy:1148
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_5ecec5c0:

    # m "For me, it's just a nice launch pad to six figures."
    m "對我來說，這是我的薪水達到六位數字的好出發點。"

# game/day2.rpy:1150
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_5fa7b338:

    # p "Is it possible to withstand long hours with that approach?"
    p "你覺得你這樣想能夠忍受長時間的工作嗎？"

# game/day2.rpy:1152
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_456ee605:

    # m "Eventually, I'll get used to it."
    m "我會越來越習慣。"

# game/day2.rpy:1154
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_9cc58f01:

    # m "After all, hard work is what I'm really good at..."
    m "畢竟，我很善於努力……"

# game/day2.rpy:1156
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_b5ea5349:

    # m "Yeah... really good."
    m "對……真的很好。"

# game/day2.rpy:1158
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_72f64744:

    # p "Hey, did I ask anything wrong?"
    p "嘿，我問錯了什麼問題嗎？"

# game/day2.rpy:1160
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_e612037c:

    # m "..."
    m "……"

# game/day2.rpy:1162
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_6be46b0e:

    # m "No, it's just... I really don't like to lie."
    m "沒有，就是……我很不喜歡說謊。"

# game/day2.rpy:1164
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_71d39a65:

    # m "And right now I'm lying not only to you, but also to myself."
    m "而現在我不但對你說謊，而且對我自己說謊。"

# game/day2.rpy:1166
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_9752945e:

    # m "I don't want any office job at all, be it the six or zero figures one."
    m "我不想要辦公室的工作，無論工資有多少。"

# game/day2.rpy:1168
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_db1dc562:

    # m "It's brutally boring, and I'll be working with mediocre people."
    m "辦公室工作無聊死了，我也要跟平凡人一起工作。"

# game/day2.rpy:1170
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_495b8b67:

    # p "Mediocre? The jobs you just mentioned are for the very best..."
    p "平凡人？你剛才說的工作都隻有最佳員工才能……"

# game/day2.rpy:1172
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_9031a3d7:

    # m "The very best of those who can only work for someone else."
    m "任職於其他人的最佳員工。"

# game/day2.rpy:1174
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_507158a8:

    # m "Truly outstanding people play by their own rules."
    m "真是非凡的人都是按自己的規則行事。"

# game/day2.rpy:1176
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_db24f0fe:

    # p "Well then, why go for..."
    p "那樣，你何不……"

# game/day2.rpy:1178
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_65f1fb3b:

    # m "You don't understand, huh? You clearly don't, do you..."
    m "你真的不理解，是嗎？你明明根本就不明白……"

# game/day2.rpy:1180
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_10f594eb:

    # m "A corporate job is the only option for me as I'm not special."
    m "因為我不特別，所以我不得已隻好做公司的工作。"

# game/day2.rpy:1182
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_e0f56767:

    # p "Hey, don't be self-loathing."
    p "嘿，你別那麼自我貶低。"

# game/day2.rpy:1184
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_2f778ba5:

    # m "I'm only being honest... I hate how \"everyone is special\" nowadays."
    m "說實話而已……我很討厭這個\“每個人都很特別”\的說法。"

# game/day2.rpy:1186
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_7fbf007a:

    # m "Why? Why do they tell that to kids? It only makes them suffer..."
    m "為什麼？他們為什麼會給小孩說這一句話？這隻會讓他們傷心……"

# game/day2.rpy:1188
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_395ead92:

    # p "Well, {i}because{/i} they're kids... To support them."
    p "那就是因為是小孩，而說的……為了支持他們。"

# game/day2.rpy:1190
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_19351c1e:

    # m "Then it should be \"do your best\" instead of \"you're special\"."
    m "那，應該說\"盡心盡力\"，而不是\"你很特別\"。"

# game/day2.rpy:1192
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_322ee15a:

    # m "If you only excel at studying, and teachers assure you of bright future ahead..."
    m "如果你隻善於學習，而且老師都保証你生活中將有精彩的未來……"

# game/day2.rpy:1194
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_3ebdb7a6:

    # m "It only means you're nothing special, just like them. Just like me..."
    m "這就是說明你沒什麼特別的，就像他們一樣。就像我一樣……"

# game/day2.rpy:1196
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_b11dfdb8:

    # m "I'm a queen of mediocrity."
    m "我是平庸的女王。"

# game/day2.rpy:1198
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_b670eeaa:

    # m "You won't believe how jealous I am of someone with raw, natural talent."
    m "你想象不了我多麼羨慕有自然天賦的天才的人。"

# game/day2.rpy:1199
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_da0c156a:

    # m "It's the only way to be number one."
    m "這是當作第一名的唯一的辦法。"

# game/day2.rpy:1201
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_a446cc6b:

    # p "I see where you're going, but raw talent is a waste if not honed."
    p "我明白你的意思，可是要是不磨練，自然的天賦就算是浪費了。"

# game/day2.rpy:1202
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_f546b65d:

    # p "And talented people are often lazy, so if you work more, you can catch up!"
    p "再說，有才能的人常常很懶。所以隻要你比他們努力得多，就能配得上。"

# game/day2.rpy:1204
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_fafceeb0:

    # m "Only if there's enough time."
    m "隻有在時間夠的條件下，才可以。"

# game/day2.rpy:1206
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_a54aa352:

    # m "Sadly, I'm already behind... I hate it, I really do!"
    m "很可惜，我已經落下了……很討厭，真的非常討厭！"

# game/day2.rpy:1207
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_95b75489:

    # p "You're kidding me."
    p "你應該是開玩笑。"

# game/day2.rpy:1209
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_729520c2:

    # m "I'm afraid not."
    m "才沒有。"

# game/day2.rpy:1211
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_95a6be1f:

    # m "Say, if I wanted to go into figure skating..."
    m "比如說，我想開始花樣滑冰……"

# game/day2.rpy:1212
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_8bfc207a:

    # p "Isn't this a bit of an extreme example?"
    p "你不覺得你的這個例子有一點極端嗎？"

# game/day2.rpy:1214
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_75dba3c2:

    # m "Okay, let's talk about drawing. I always wanted to be good at it."
    m "那好，我們講畫畫怎麼樣？我總是覺得自己會畫畫。"

# game/day2.rpy:1216
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_0bbe3afa:

    # m "If I start now, in two years I'll be pretty decent..."
    m "要是我現在開始，兩年后我應該已經畫得很不錯……"

# game/day2.rpy:1218
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_737c3f3d:

    # m "But those who started ten years ago will be presented in art galleries."
    m "但是，十年前開始的人已經會在博物館展出他們的作品。"

# game/day2.rpy:1220
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_d0f6e2e0:

    # m "But the punchline is..."
    m "但是，最可笑的是……"

# game/day2.rpy:1222
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_c5597036:

    # m "These art galleries would {i}always{/i} be named after someone with raw talent."
    m "那些博物館都要以有自然天賦的人命名。"

# game/day2.rpy:1224
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_71e41244:

    # p "Trust me, you still have enough time, Marta!"
    p "你可以相信我，你還有很多時間，瑪莎！"

# game/day2.rpy:1226
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_1511cc76:

    # m "Maybe, but I really need to make up my mind and concentrate on... something."
    m "也許吧。不過，我真需要下定決心把我的注意力集中到……某些事情。"

# game/day2.rpy:1228
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_0069a007:

    # m "\"Something\"... Screw it, I have zero idea about what I want to do!"
    m "\"某些事情\"……我去，未來要做什麼我一點主意也沒有！"

# game/day2.rpy:1229
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_31c89ee8:

    # p "Well, have you tried discussing it with your parents?"
    p "你試過跟你的父母討論這個問題嗎？"

# game/day2.rpy:1231
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_c3135a60:

    # m "I despise them."
    m "我覺得沒有什麼用。"

# game/day2.rpy:1233
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_db1f5e1a:

    # p "Why?"
    p "為什麼？"

# game/day2.rpy:1235
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_103a07fd:

    # m "My father settled down and tried to drag me along."
    m "我父親平靜下來了，而且也認同我和他一樣。"

# game/day2.rpy:1237
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_53804468:

    # m "I asked countless times to get me into arts, dancing, whatever..."
    m "無數次我請求他給我報名跳舞班、藝術班什麼的……"

# game/day2.rpy:1239
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_49ad74a0:

    # m "You know, just to try it out and see if it's my thing."
    m "你知道，為了我能嘗試並了解這到底適不適合我。"

# game/day2.rpy:1240
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_e756c059:

    # m "He always told me I should forget this nonsense and study hard."
    m "他總是跟我說我應該忘掉那些傻事，而把我的努力都集中到學習。"

# game/day2.rpy:1242
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_9dc5cceb:

    # m "To live a decent life, he said..."
    m "為了有體面的未來，他說……"

# game/day2.rpy:1244
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_1b05d60d:

    # m "And my mother... I don't even know her well. But that's another story."
    m "我的母親呢……我不大知道她是什麼樣的人。但是，這是另外的故事。"

# game/day2.rpy:1245
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_38d97d88:

    # p "I don't know what to say..."
    p "我不知道該說什麼……"

# game/day2.rpy:1247
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_acd9e505:

    # m "Well, excuse me for this rant."
    m "抱歉我一下子說了那麼多。"

# game/day2.rpy:1249
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_3777be7b:

    # m "Actually, thanks for listening. I feel a bit better now!"
    m "實際上，謝謝你的傾聽。現在感覺好多了！"

# game/day2.rpy:1251
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_7d873c52:

    # m "Hey, why are you looking at me like that, [player_name]?"
    m "吶，你為什麼那樣看著我嗎，[player_name]？"

# game/day2.rpy:1253
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_4c64c484:

    # m "Don't think I opened up or anything."
    m "你是不是不想我對你傾訴什麼的。"

# game/day2.rpy:1254
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_e2d59fe4:

    # p "I just go over what you said, Marta."
    p "我在考慮你說的話，瑪莎。"

# game/day2.rpy:1256
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_f7f2af80:

    # m "Really? Well then, take your time!"
    m "真的嗎？那你別著急啦！"

# game/day2.rpy:1258
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_5e93503a:

    # m "You're walking painfully slow anyway."
    m "反正，你應該思考得非常痛苦且遲緩。"

# game/day2.rpy:1259
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_09fbe708:

    # m "See you tomorrow!"
    m "明天見！"

# game/day2.rpy:1261
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_marta_830a0976:

    # m "I... I'll be glad to see you tomorrow..."
    m "我……明天再見再見到你時會很高興的……"

# game/day2.rpy:1268
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_a56a9b4d:

    # "It's Nana."
    "這便是娜娜。"

# game/day2.rpy:1269
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_28ad94ac:

    # "She says nothing, just standing around."
    "他不說話，隻是站在那。"

# game/day2.rpy:1270
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_a20cefa7:

    # "..."
    "……"

# game/day2.rpy:1271
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_7bf4e082:

    # "Not being fond of staring contests, I decide to say something first."
    "不喜歡盯著比賽的我試圖打算先開始對話。"

# game/day2.rpy:1272
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_c364a80c:

    # p "Hey, how're you?"
    p "嗨，你怎麼樣？"

# game/day2.rpy:1273
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_bb2cf764:

    # n "..."
    n "……"

# game/day2.rpy:1274
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_e392db5c:

    # p "Ready for the..."
    p "你准備好了……"

# game/day2.rpy:1276
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_3b618e05:

    # n "Career day tomorrow? Sure I am!"
    n "明天的事業日嗎？肯定的！"

# game/day2.rpy:1278
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_ccf25334:

    # p "Is there..."
    p "出了什麼事……"

# game/day2.rpy:1280
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_c828182a:

    # n "Anything wrong? No, it's alright, thanks for asking!"
    n "沒出什麼事，一切都好，謝謝你的關心！"

# game/day2.rpy:1282
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_fcab2fd5:

    # p "Nana, you're acting strange."
    p "娜娜，你的行為很詭異。"

# game/day2.rpy:1283
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_bb2cf764_1:

    # n "..."
    n "……"

# game/day2.rpy:1285
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_9dcff657:

    # n "I'm sorry... You have nothing to do with it."
    n "對不起……你和這件事無關。"

# game/day2.rpy:1287
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_4f571819:

    # p "What happened?"
    p "什麼事？"

# game/day2.rpy:1289
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_4926b5d3:

    # n "Don't think you'll understand, [player_name]."
    n "我覺得你不會理解，[player_name]。"

# game/day2.rpy:1291
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_a5e90435:

    # p "Can't say unless I give it a try."
    p "不試試我怎麼會知道。"

# game/day2.rpy:1293
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_f000e5ac:

    # n "Well, if you insist..."
    n "好，如果你堅持……"

# game/day2.rpy:1295
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_1db66cc8:

    # n "I can't take it anymore... People are so scripted!"
    n "我忍受不了……人們都喜歡照著稿子念！"

# game/day2.rpy:1297
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_37761e5a:

    # p "Scripted? Predictable, you mean?"
    p "照著稿子念是什麼意思？容易預測的嗎？"

# game/day2.rpy:1299
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_2ed5aff4:

    # n "Yes, to put it mildly..."
    n "是的，說得婉轉些……"

# game/day2.rpy:1301
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_146dbe8b:

    # n "Have you ever played a role-playing game, [player_name]?"
    n "你玩過角色扮演游戲嗎，[player_name]？"

# game/day2.rpy:1302
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_dfa52cc3:

    # p "Um..."
    p "嗯……"

# game/day2.rpy:1304
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_206db95e:

    # n "Hey, not {i}that{/i} kind of a game, you silly!"
    n "嘿，我說的不是你想的那一種，傻瓜！"

# game/day2.rpy:1306
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_56231a3e:

    # n "A computer game where you have a few main characters, a side cast..."
    n "是一種電子游戲，它一般有幾個主人公，幾個配角……"

# game/day2.rpy:1308
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_a4fffa04:

    # n "And then a lot of non-playable characters to enrich the game lore."
    n "還有很多豐富游戲世界的npc。"

# game/day2.rpy:1310
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_d9878766:

    # n "Your interaction with the latter is limited to just a couple of phrases..."
    n "你跟npc的交流一般限制到幾句話……"

# game/day2.rpy:1312
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_abe45263:

    # n "It's because they're usually scripted only to serve a certain game purpose."
    n "這是因為他們是為了實現一定的游戲目的而存在，被提前寫好劇本的。"

# game/day2.rpy:1314
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_ddec541d:

    # n "Guess what, it seems that our life is no different."
    n "沒想到吧，但是好像我們的人生好像也都差不多一樣。"

# game/day2.rpy:1315
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_5f815775:

    # p "What do you mean?"
    p "這是什麼意思呢？"

# game/day2.rpy:1317
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_3edda697:

    # n "I think eighty percent of people, if not more, are non-playable characters."
    n "我覺得有百分之八十的人都是固定人物。"

# game/day2.rpy:1318
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_cb094458:

    # p "C'mon, it's not true..."
    p "哦，拜托，不會是這樣的……"

# game/day2.rpy:1320
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_d914c986:

    # n "Maybe I'm wrong, but then tell me... why are they so shallow?"
    n "我也許是錯的，那你告訴我……他們為什麼那麼膚淺？"

# game/day2.rpy:1322
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_99f3ba10:

    # n "Try to throw in an unconventional reply when chatting to these people..."
    n "你跟那些人聊天的時候，你一次試試給他們不合常規的回答……"

# game/day2.rpy:1324
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_869efdcf:

    # n "Next thing you know, there's that particularly blank expression in their eyes."
    n "他們就露出這種很特殊的惶恐的眼神。"

# game/day2.rpy:1326
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_87a00c64:

    # n "You broke the script, and they're not programmed to handle that."
    n "你把劇本打破了，他們就不知道該怎麼辦了。"

# game/day2.rpy:1327
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_ac6852c3:

    # p "Oh wow, Nana... At least now it's clear why you were silent in the beginning."
    p "哇，娜娜……至少我終於明白你為什麼起先那麼不好說話。"

# game/day2.rpy:1329
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_0e0a49ae:

    # n "\"Ready for the career day tomorrow?\""
    n "\"准備好了明天的事業日嗎？\""

# game/day2.rpy:1331
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_95087551:

    # n "If I say yes, would you be delighted? If I say no, would you offer immediate help?"
    n "我說有，你會高興嗎？我說沒有，你會提供立刻的幫助嗎？"

# game/day2.rpy:1333
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_a9d27ebc:

    # n "I doubt it. Truth is, only expected a reply that'd abide by the script."
    n "我很懷疑。但真相就是，唯一恰當的回答是那個符合劇本的。"

# game/day2.rpy:1335
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_55047463:

    # n "Something you could reply to with \"Oh, I see\" and all."
    n "一個你會給\"嗯，那好\"之類的回答。"

# game/day2.rpy:1336
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_f49a2276:

    # p "Well, how do you expect me to communicate?"
    p "那，你希望我怎麼交流？"

# game/day2.rpy:1338
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_c4c1e4f8:

    # n "I'd expect anyone, you included, to keep silent if there's nothing to say."
    n "我希望包括你在內所有的人，當沒什麼值得說出來的話，那就不要說話。"

# game/day2.rpy:1340
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_bcda9b7b:

    # n "People just can't shut up, and you know why?"
    n "人們絕對不能閉嘴！你知道是為什麼嗎？"

# game/day2.rpy:1342
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_54c9499c:

    # n "Because they're afraid to start thinking instead of talking."
    n "因為他們害怕當停止說話的時候必須要開始思考。"

# game/day2.rpy:1344
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_00aaa220:

    # n "Thinking process can lead to a rather unpleasant self-realization..."
    n "思維過程會令人發現他們不願意承認的事情……"

# game/day2.rpy:1345
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_90a7736a:

    # n "That is, how shallow you are. This kills the non-playable character."
    n "就是，你有多麼膚淺。這種發現就會殺死固定的人物。"

# game/day2.rpy:1347
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_d3f80e21:

    # p "What's so bad about discussing something conventional... like hobbies?"
    p "談普通的事情為什麼一定是不好的？例如，談愛好？"

# game/day2.rpy:1349
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_a6d6eef6:

    # n "Nothing, but then it goes down the same alley."
    n "沒什麼不好的，就是效果都是一樣的。"

# game/day2.rpy:1351
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_7613bf00:

    # n "Music? No one knows anything outside the top charts."
    n "談音樂？音樂排行榜之外，人們就什麼都不知道。"

# game/day2.rpy:1352
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_3e0cbaa2:

    # n "Movies? Same, people only watch what's trending today."
    n "談電影？一樣的，人人隻看符合潮流的一些。"

# game/day2.rpy:1354
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_032d4407:

    # n "\"Trending\" is the keyword here."
    n "\"潮流\"是關鍵的。"

# game/day2.rpy:1356
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_61b5ed37:

    # n "Non-playable characters don't have hobbies, they follow the trend."
    n "固定人物沒有愛好，他們隻會趕潮流。"

# game/day2.rpy:1357
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_3167bf17:

    # p "Now that you mention it... Internet subculture is going mainstream..."
    p "你現在說到這個問題……確實網絡文化越來越主流……"

# game/day2.rpy:1359
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_c797a566:

    # n "We're the meme generation, [player_name]."
    n "我們是模因的一代，[player_name]。"

# game/day2.rpy:1362
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_eca6df72:

    # n "It's even worse when they start enjoying {i}my{/i} hobbies."
    n "更可惡的是他們喜歡上我的愛好的時候。"

# game/day2.rpy:1363
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_a5156bf6:

    # p "What're you into?"
    p "你喜歡什麼？"

# game/day2.rpy:1364
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_80129244:

    # n "Swimming, for instance."
    n "比如說，游泳。"

# game/day2.rpy:1365
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_be2abced:

    # p "So what if swimming becomes the next hot topic?"
    p "所以你說游泳成下一個熱門的話題是不好的嗎？"

# game/day2.rpy:1366
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_a88ae799:

    # n "Then my local pool will be crowded with people who can't swim at all."
    n "那樣，我家附近的游泳池會充滿根本不會游泳的人。"

# game/day2.rpy:1367
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_5850e2be:

    # n "They don't even want to learn, they're here because everyone else is."
    n "他們甚至不想學習。大家都來，他們就也來了。"

# game/day2.rpy:1368
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_4240b1bd:

    # n "I'd close that pool for being too shallow."
    n "可以的話，我就關閉這個游泳池，因為它太淺了。"

# game/day2.rpy:1370
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_2734b3c6:

    # p "Jeez, Nana, isn't it a bit too much?"
    p "哎呀，娜娜，你不覺得這樣說太過分了嗎？"

# game/day2.rpy:1371
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_560d2be4:

    # p "You're simply calling the majority of people fools."
    p "你正試圖把部分的人稱呼笨蛋。"

# game/day2.rpy:1373
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_48e14e29:

    # n "I've never ever called them like that."
    n "我沒有這麼說·。"

# game/day2.rpy:1375
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_21202f6e:

    # n "In a way, they are the smarter ones, as they fit in seamlessly."
    n "從一方面，他們更聰明，能相處得非常那麼融洽。"

# game/day2.rpy:1377
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_9d189d48:

    # n "While I... I just stand out like a sore thumb."
    n "我呢……顯而易見。"

# game/day2.rpy:1379
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_bb2cf764_2:

    # n "..."
    n "……"

# game/day2.rpy:1381
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_1ed66a90:

    # n "My, I've actually gone a bit too far."
    n "天哪，真是過分了點。"

# game/day2.rpy:1383
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_828733f3:

    # n "Please don't take what I said close to heart, alright?"
    n "請別放在心上，好嗎？"

# game/day2.rpy:1385
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_56045dae:

    # n "I'm a bit ashamed of this confession."
    n "我對這個坦白感到羞愧。"

# game/day2.rpy:1386
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_99dc1f93:

    # p "Well, sorry for scripted replies, I guess."
    p "抱歉我那符合劇本的回答……"

# game/day2.rpy:1388
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_5c07db18:

    # n "You're not like that."
    n "你不是那樣的人。"

# game/day2.rpy:1390
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_cbae397a:

    # n "I'm even thinking... You know, it's just a maybe!"
    n "有時候我想……你知道，這隻是一個可能！"

# game/day2.rpy:1392
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_6ea79671:

    # n "Maybe my life gets less boring every time I talk to you."
    n "可能，我跟你說話的時候，我的生活變得不那麼沒意思。"

# game/day2.rpy:1394
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_b57b2df7:

    # n "You made me light up a bit. Thanks!"
    n "你讓我開心了一點，謝謝你！"

# game/day2.rpy:1396
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_nana_7e0666d9:

    # n "Looking forward to see you tomorrow!"
    n "忍不住說明天見！"

# game/day2.rpy:1402
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_e1c876aa:

    # "It's Sima."
    "這是希瑪。"

# game/day2.rpy:1404
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_860d4de1:

    # s "Hi, [player_name]."
    s "你好，[player_name]。"

# game/day2.rpy:1405
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_62698bfa:

    # s "From a distance, it looks like you don't know where to go."
    s "從遠處看， 你似乎不知道該去哪兒。"

# game/day2.rpy:1406
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_16188a8e:

    # p "Doesn't matter as long as you keep me company."
    p "隻要跟你一起，我都無所謂。"

# game/day2.rpy:1408
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_b2dcfe05:

    # s "Oh..."
    s "哦……"

# game/day2.rpy:1410
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_4c5ee4db:

    # s "How's your week going, [player_name]?"
    s "這個星期你怎麼樣，[player_name]？"

# game/day2.rpy:1412
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_5ebd49cc:

    # p "Going great! Just a little bit tired..."
    p "非常好！就是，有一點困……"

# game/day2.rpy:1414
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_816846c8:

    # s "Get some rest so you'll be ready for career day."
    s "休息一下，然后明天的事業日就能過得順利。"

# game/day2.rpy:1416
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_7da7a19f:

    # p "Excited about it?"
    p "興奮嗎？"

# game/day2.rpy:1418
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_0c1ea92c:

    # s "I am! I am..."
    s "是的！我……"

# game/day2.rpy:1420
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_e1554201:

    # s "..."
    s "……"

# game/day2.rpy:1421
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_71e15efb:

    # p "Did I say something wrong?"
    p "我說錯了話嗎？"

# game/day2.rpy:1423
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_0e658d4a:

    # s "Nothing at all! It's just... you see..."
    s "根本沒有！隻是……你看……"

# game/day2.rpy:1425
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_97fe97a6:

    # s "I'm in a constant fear of missing out."
    s "我總是很怕錯過機會。"

# game/day2.rpy:1427
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_5f815775:

    # p "What do you mean?"
    p "什麼意思？"

# game/day2.rpy:1429
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_a5631348:

    # s "I always think I should've been busy with something else."
    s "我一直都在想我也許該做另外一件事情。"

# game/day2.rpy:1431
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_ff670172:

    # s "Maybe I should've gone to another school?"
    s "還是，該去另外一個學校？"

# game/day2.rpy:1433
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_0ba5fc25:

    # s "A few years ago I declined an invitation for a movie audition..."
    s "幾年前，我拒絕一個電影試演的邀請……"

# game/day2.rpy:1435
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_86772307:

    # s "What if I missed the opportunity of a lifetime?"
    s "要是那時候錯過了我一輩子的機會呢？"

# game/day2.rpy:1437
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_8cd11eda:

    # s "Tomorrow won't be any different."
    s "明天也會是這樣的。"

# game/day2.rpy:1439
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_3f7955b6:

    # s "I know it probably sounds laughable..."
    s "我知道這聽起來應該很可笑……"

# game/day2.rpy:1440
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_dc3e9835:

    # p "Is there anything to laugh about?"
    p "那裡有什麼可笑的？"

# game/day2.rpy:1442
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_dbd3aaf4:

    # s "Trust me, there is, simply because..."
    s "相信我吧，有很多。這就是因為……"

# game/day2.rpy:1444
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_22f6520d:

    # s "\"Nothing matters very much, and few things matter at all.\""
    s "\"沒什麼特別需要在意的事情，而且很少的事情才需要在意。\""

# game/day2.rpy:1446
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_e4e13823:

    # p "Care to explain?"
    p "你不想解釋一下？"

# game/day2.rpy:1448
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_574e338c:

    # s "Well, it's a long story... Maybe next time, [player_name]."
    s "故事很長……也許下次吧，[player_name]。"

# game/day2.rpy:1450
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_3cca7477:

    # s "By the way, I'm a root of that fear for some. Funny, isn't it?"
    s "再說，我自己是因為別人才有這種害怕的原因。很有意思，你不覺得嗎？"

# game/day2.rpy:1452
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_5f815775_1:

    # p "What do you mean?"
    p "什麼意思呢？"

# game/day2.rpy:1454
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_fbb7aa48:

    # s "Others often think they miss out on something {i}I{/i} do."
    s "別人常常會想他們錯過了我做的某些事。"

# game/day2.rpy:1456
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_c35fd3aa:

    # s "If I stay late studying, so that the next day I have dark circles under my eyes..."
    s "有的時候我學習睡得很晚，所以下一天我有黑眼圈兒……"

# game/day2.rpy:1458
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_8c7e726a:

    # s "Other girls would gossip about me spending the whole night out."
    s "其他女孩會說閑話說我昨天出去浪了一夜。"

# game/day2.rpy:1460
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_22a08019:

    # s "If they invite me somewhere, and I'm busy, they think that I simply reject them."
    s "要是他們叫我跟她們一起出去玩，而我很忙，她們就會以為我拒絕她們。"

# game/day2.rpy:1462
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_605c1fc2:

    # s "That I have something better to do."
    s "以為我有更好玩的事情。"

# game/day2.rpy:1464
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_eb72b9ed:

    # s "See why is it so amusing?"
    s "你能理解這為什麼那麼有意思嗎？"

# game/day2.rpy:1466
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_ed28affb:

    # s "They're envious about missing out on something they imagine I'm doing..."
    s "她們羨慕我做她們以為我在做的事情……"

# game/day2.rpy:1468
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_4650dffe:

    # s "Something that doesn't even exist."
    s "實際上不存在的事情。"

# game/day2.rpy:1470
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_282f8165:

    # s "They also say they can't understand me... that I look reserved."
    s "她們也會說她們不理解我……我看起來很拘謹。"

# game/day2.rpy:1472
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_0f52a276:

    # s "In the end, they stop approaching me altogether... I'm not reserved!"
    s "最終，她們完全不再來找我而已……可是，我不拘謹！"

# game/day2.rpy:1474
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_1bc4aa37:

    # s "It's simply my everyday expression! I'm sorry, you know!"
    s "這隻是我臉上經常的表情！我很抱歉，你知道的！"

# game/day2.rpy:1476
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_4952e0b2:

    # s "Sorry that I don't look like your average cheerleader..."
    s "很抱歉我不像普通的拉拉隊員……"

# game/day2.rpy:1478
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_f5d3effc:

    # p "Wow... I mean, I'd think you're very popular if we just met..."
    p "哇……要是我們剛才認識的話，我就會以為你很受歡迎……"

# game/day2.rpy:1480
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_f9a98043:

    # s "That's exactly what everyone assumes, [player_name]."
    s "這就是大家都以為的，[player_name]。"

# game/day2.rpy:1482
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_d4fa9fd9:

    # s "Oh well, it only means I should treasure those who see the real me."
    s "不過，這隻意味著我要很舍不得能看見真實面目的人。"

# game/day2.rpy:1484
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_63f8fc68:

    # p "I'd be happy to learn more about the real you, Sima."
    p "我很樂意更多理解真實的你，希瑪。"

# game/day2.rpy:1486
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_584030bd:

    # s "Is that so?"
    s "真的嗎？"

# game/day2.rpy:1488
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_693ec91e:

    # s "What if you simply lose the interest after a while?"
    s "要是過了一會兒你對我失去興趣呢？"

# game/day2.rpy:1490
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_45df0ea9:

    # s "What if you find me pretty boring?"
    s "如果你認為我很無聊呢？"

# game/day2.rpy:1492
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_d0bd4aec:

    # s "It'd be painful, [player_name]."
    s "我會很傷心的，[player_name]。"

# game/day2.rpy:1494
translate chinese_trad day2_road_home_sima_02a67159:

    # s "I hate losing people after I grow accustomed to them."
    s "我很討厭跟他們熟悉后失去的人。"

